# 14. What file contains the local DNS entries?(RED)
# 
# /etc/hosts
#
# man host: host name data base.
# The host file contains information regarding the known hosts on the network. For each
# host a single line should be present with the following information:
# 	Internet address
#	Official host name
#	Aliases
#
# [xtang@c2r1p3]/etc>cat hosts
# 10.51.1.10       cdn.42.fr
# 10.51.1.10    cdn.intra.42.fr
# 127.0.0.1       localhost
# 255.255.255.255 broadcasthost
# ::1             localhost
